          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Campaign Lifecycle -->
    <details class="mb-6 group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer font-heading font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <span>3. Campaign Lifecycle</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-text-secondary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-4 pb-4">
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">Every campaign follows a lifecycle. Knowing which phase you are in determines which tools to use.</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Diagnosis</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Define the problem with evidence. Research, PAIA requests, field monitoring.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Framing</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Win the narrative before government does. Media, community testimony, social media.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Demand</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Put a specific, concrete ask on record. Demand letter, parliamentary submission.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Escalation</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Increase the cost of non-compliance. Litigation threat, mobilisation, media blitz.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">5</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Negotiation</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Convert pressure into commitment. Bilaterals, mediated dialogue, signed agreements.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">6</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Monitoring</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Hold government to promises. Progress tracking, field verification, published scorecards.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-blue-600 text-white font-heading font-bold text-xs flex items-center justify-center">7</span>
            <div><p class="font-semibold text-sm">Consolidation</p><p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Embed the win in policy or law. Policy brief, legislative submission, budget tracking.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Accountability Scorecard -->
    <details class="mb-6 group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer font-heading font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <span>4. The Accountability Scorecard</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-text-secondary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-4 pb-4">
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">A published scorecard transforms abstract advocacy into a specific, recurring accountability moment. Government knows it is coming. Media knows when to ask questions.</p>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm mb-2">Design Principles</h4>
        <ul class="text-text-secondary text-sm space-y-1 list-disc pl-5 mb-4">
          <li>Use government's <strong>own commitments</strong> as the measure — APPs, Budget Vote speeches, court orders</li>
          <li><strong>RAG rating</strong>: Green = met, Amber = partial/delayed, Red = no delivery</li>
          <li>Publish <strong>before</strong> government publishes its APR — do not let them set the narrative</li>
          <li>Make it <strong>visual</strong> and shareable on WhatsApp</li>
          <li>Include a <strong>trend line</strong> — year-on-year comparison is the most powerful tool</li>
        </ul>
        <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm mb-2">Sample Indicators (Education)</h4>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-xs border-collapse">
            <thead><tr class="bg-gray-50"><th class="text-left p-2 font-heading font-semibold border-b">Indicator</th><th class="text-left p-2 font-heading font-semibold border-b">Target</th><th class="text-left p-2 font-heading font-semibold border-b">Actual</th><th class="text-left p-2 font-heading font-semibold border-b">Rating</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="p-2">Grade 1–3 workbooks delivered by Day 1</td><td class="p-2">100% by 15 Jan</td><td class="p-2">68% by end Jan</td><td class="p-2"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500" title="Red"></span></td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="p-2">Teacher vacancy rate (quintile 1–2)</td><td class="p-2">&lt; 3%</td><td class="p-2">9.2%</td><td class="p-2"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500" title="Red"></span></td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b"><td class="p-2">Schools with functional toilets</td><td class="p-2">100% by 2025</td><td class="p-2">84%</td><td class="p-2"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-amber-500" title="Amber"></span></td></tr>
              <tr><td class="p-2">ASIDI schools completed per year</td><td class="p-2">100% of plan</td><td class="p-2">61%</td><td class="p-2"><span class="inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500" title="Red"></span></td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- Campaign Case Studies -->
    <details class="mb-6 group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
