        <span>5. Campaign Case Studies</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-text-secondary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
      </summary>
      <div class="px-4 pb-4 space-y-5">
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
          <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm">A. Mother-Tongue Literacy in Foundation Phase</h4>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-xs mt-1">PIRLS 2021: 81% of Grade 4 learners cannot read for meaning. Coalition led by PRAESA, with Stellenbosch ReSEP, SECTION27, and rural CBOs. Demand letters sent; negotiating binding timelines for Home Language Policy implementation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
          <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm">B. School Safety &amp; Gender-Based Violence</h4>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-xs mt-1">Estimated 1 in 3 learners affected by SRGBV. Shadow review found only 7% of schools had a functional safety committee. PAIA requests to all 9 PEDs for misconduct records. Secured joint sitting of Education and Justice Portfolio Committees.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-4">
          <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-sm">C. Rapid Response: Textbook Non-Delivery Crisis</h4>
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-xs mt-1">72-hour response protocol: field data compiled within 4 hours, public statement released, demand letter to DBE DG at 12 hours, parliamentary questions at 24 hours, full evidence brief at 48–72 hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </details>

    <!-- 30-Day Launch -->
    <details class="mb-6 group border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer font-heading font-semibold text-text-primary hover:bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
        <span>6. Launch a Coalition in 30 Days</span>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-text-secondary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
